After my Fiverr experience I&rsquo;ll update this snippet or add a new one, ideally one full of margin notes.
Update (same day): I&rsquo;m back! I didn&rsquo;t use Fiverr. I used the post on capnfabs for reference and set up margin notes myself. Thank you Fabian for documenting your process.3 I&rsquo;ll have to learn to use Fiverr another day.
I&rsquo;m glad to have this working. There&rsquo;s room to improve the style though. Perhaps in a future iteration I&rsquo;ll move the main content left to give more space for the margin notes, or make some changes to the font and size.
